text: Andrew Law may refer to: * Andrew Bonar Law (1858-1923), British prime minister, from 1922 * Andrew Law (financier) (born 1966), British hedge fund executive * Andrew Law (composer) (1749-1821), American composer and preacher * Andrew Law (artist) (1873-1967), Scottish artist * Michael Andrew Law (born 1982), Hong Kong artist ==See also== * Law (surname) * Law (disambiguation)
